  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd9\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dbb\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d85\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0da0\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two directors remanded who gave check worth Rs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage today (22) ordered that a director and a director of a leading private company in Sri Lanka, who were arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department for defrauding five and a half million rupees by saying that they would give US dollars, be remanded until the 31st.",
        "Dharmapriya Bandara Dasanayake and Anushki Samadhi Pradinandu were thus remanded in custody.",
        "These facts were presented when these suspects were arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department today while staying at a hotel in Tarupaha, Colombo and presented to the court.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department also presented the facts to the court that these suspects had given two valuable checks saying that they would give US dollars.",
        "According to a complaint made by Mr. Garcia Punchiheva, the investigation into the incident was carried out and the suspects were arrested five years later, the Criminal Investigation Department presented the facts to the court."
      ],
